video.title: America's Next Top Model
video.synopsis: Supermodel Tyra Banks created and executive-produced this reality series that chronicles the transformation of young women into potential supermodels.

episodes.synopsis: In Los Angeles, 31 guys and girls pair off to see which couple can take the best selfie while walking a runway. Later comes the first round of cuts.
episodes.title: The Boyz R Back

episodes.synopsis: The semifinalists compete in a race against time in a subway challenge, and then head to the beach for a more relaxing photo session.
episodes.title: The Guy Who Gets a Second Chance

episodes.synopsis: The final 14 settle into their new home, where tensions immediately erupt. A challenge forces them to wear nothing but Silly String.
episodes.title: The Girl Who's a Player

episodes.synopsis: An optical illusion photo shoot proves challenging. One of the models isn't thrilled with her makeover. A spur-of-the-moment kiss sparks a debate.
episodes.title: The Guy Who Gets a Beard Weave

episodes.synopsis: Tyra teaches the group how to seduce a camera. One of the models commits a major violation, and a low challenge score puts another at risk.
episodes.title: The Guy Who Starts a Fight

episodes.synopsis: During a wind-blown photo shoot, one of the models struggles to redeem herself. A celebrity guest issues a team challenge involving an ad campaign.
episodes.title: The Girl Who Got Five Frames

episodes.synopsis: The contestants put their acting skills to the test to win a TV role. An unusual pairing sparks jealousy, while an overheard comment rocks the house.
episodes.title: The Guy Who Wears Heels

episodes.synopsis: After receiving harsh feedback from Kelly Cutrone during a team challenge, two models rethink their relationship. The DNA test results are revealed.
episodes.title: The Girl Who Says: It's Over

episodes.synopsis: The models attend castings for fashion week. One still has trouble letting loose; another can't contain her temper. A travel destination is revealed.
episodes.title: The Guy Who Wows Betsey Johnson

episodes.synopsis: An eliminated model gets a second chance, and then irritates the group. The contestants are challenged to remain composed during a creepy photo shoot.
episodes.title: The Girl with the Bloodcurdling Scream

episodes.synopsis: Before the seven remaining models depart Los Angeles for their travel destination, new behind-the-scenes clips from the first 10 episodes are shown.
episodes.title: What Happens on ANTM Stays on ANTM

episodes.synopsis: The models compete in a dance challenge, coached and judged by a boy band. One is chastised for being controlling, another for drinking too much.
episodes.title: The Guy Who Parties Too Hard

episodes.synopsis: The contestants race against the clock and throughout the city during the go-see challenge, and one of the models is caught in an embarrassing lie.
episodes.title: The Girl Who Gets Caught in a Lie

episodes.synopsis: In the next challenge, the models act out a bilingual scene with TV soap stars. Afterward, they become Elvis Presley and Marilyn Monroe for a shoot.
episodes.title: The Guy with Moves Like Elvis

episodes.synopsis: The final four shoot a commercial for Tyra's new cosmetics line. With $100,000 at stake in the last photo session, the models give it their best shot.
episodes.title: Finale Part One: The Last Girl Standing

episodes.synopsis: In a final bid to become this cycle's top model, the three remaining contestants battle it out in a runway fashion show for an international designer.
episodes.title: Finale Part Two: America's Next Top Model Is …

episodes.synopsis: The excitement's through the roof as the hopefuls show Yu Tsai what they've got, model swimwear atop a double-decker and hit the Hollywood red carpet.
episodes.title: The Guys and Girls Make It to Hollywood

episodes.synopsis: Jonathan and Drew Scott of “Property Brothers” drop by the models' house. The surprises continue with a sudden departure and a public semi-nude shoot.
episodes.title: The Girl Who Walks Away

episodes.synopsis: Who will be dropped? The models must brave fashion's heights and walk an elevated runway. Later, Tyra coaches the bound competitors at a photo shoot.
episodes.title: The Guy Who Gets Shipped Out

episodes.synopsis: War heroes are the focus of an emotional editorial. Nyle opens up about his challenges as a Deaf model while Hadassah struggles with her Ty-over.
episodes.title: The Girl Who Has a Close Shave

episodes.synopsis: Love blossoms — and feuds flare up — among the contestants. Insecurities emerge when retouching is banned at a shoot featuring futuristic fashion.
episodes.title: The Guy Who Gets A Hickey

episodes.synopsis: Tensions are high as Mamé and Hadassah bicker. Past winner Whitney Thompson teams up with the models, who raise their game for a "fashion exorcism."
episodes.title: The Girl Who Gets Possessed

episodes.synopsis: An acting challenge forces the competitors to stretch. Later, a sexy commercial at the beach is awash with jealousy — and failed chemistry.
episodes.title: The Guy Who Acts A Fool

episodes.synopsis: The hopefuls must create a STEM PSA for harsh critics: kids. Can the models make it posing as life-size dolls — and survive a double elimination?
episodes.title: The Girl Who Got All Dolled Up

episodes.synopsis: Get set for a major face-off when the models pair up with eliminated challengers on go-sees. The  contenders must wow alongside furry canine friends.
episodes.title: The Guy or Girl Who Came Back

episodes.synopsis: Who will stay and who will go? The contestants get a jump on the competition with midair poses and then shoot a music video for Tyra's beauty line.
episodes.title: The Girl Who Became Bootyful

episodes.synopsis: Hadassah and Kelly Cutrone clash over a salon-style runway event. After a social media challenge, Mikey is called out for a focus on flirting.
episodes.title: The Guy Who Closed The Deal In Vegas

episodes.synopsis: Industry calls as the challengers craft and pitch a unique business idea. Later, a photo shoot demands that the models pose in the cold, dark woods.
episodes.title: The Girl Who Took a Shot in the Dark

episodes.synopsis: Tyra's mom enters the picture when she photographs the models and their mothers. The hopefuls pose for mock NYLON covers and meet with Chrissy Teigen.
episodes.title: The Guy Who Was a Momma’ Boy

episodes.synopsis: The finalists shoot a campaign for Zappos Couture and prepare for the last runway show. But emotions run high, and drama causes a model to lose focus.
episodes.title: Finale Part 1: The Girl Who Made a Splash

episodes.synopsis: In a runway showdown, the two finalists battle it out to earn the title. The competitors are joined by their mothers as a winner is announced.
episodes.title: Finale Part Two: America’s Next Top Model Is…

episodes.synopsis: Catch never-before-seen footage of behind-the-scenes confessions, flirtations and meltdowns.
episodes.title: And Then That Happened
